Privacy Policy
Last updated: August 03, 2024
This Privacy Policy describes Our policies and procedures on the collection, use and disclosure of Your information when You use Motivational Unicorn and tells You about Your privacy rights and how the law protects You.
We use Your Personal data to provide and improve Motivational Unicorn. By using Motivational Unicorn, You agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy has been created with the help of the Privacy Policy Generator.
Collecting and Using Your Personal Data
Types of Data Collected
Motivational Unicorn collects baseline data as outlined by Discord. We will never ask for any personal identifiable information and your data will never be shared.
Delete Your Personal Data
If you do not want any data to be shared with Motivational Unicorn, Motivational Unicorn can be removed from any of your servers that you have permission to manage. Once Motivational Unicorn is removed, you will no longer be able to use it within the server.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update Our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify You of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
We will let You know via email and/or a prominent notice on Our Service, prior to the change becoming effective and update the "Last updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy.
You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
